item.title: Google Workspace Individual accounts now have up to 1TB storage space
item.description: Google Workspace Individual accounts now have up to 1TB storage space Google has announced that it will soon introduce more features for “Workspace Individual” users, including an increase in storage capacity and advances in email personalisation for all customers.
